## Objective: Establish a test matrix for unit, integration, and end-to-end testing.

## Input: API inventory, key user paths.

## Output: Test cases, coverage reports, /docs/TESTING.md.

## example use：
```
/TEST 为 {{FEATURE}} 补齐单测（vitest/jest）+ e2e（Playwright/Detox），生成 CI 步骤。
/TEST 测试{{PROJECT}} ，生成 CI 步骤。

```

## Key Points
- Web: Playwright; RN: Detox; API: Supertest
- Mock Supabase and LLM (test doubles) to avoid real calls